AltTranslateChrome is a Chrome Extension for translating through Microsoft Translation API on the fly.
It sends words selected while pressing alt key to the API, and the translation appears in a popup balloon.
This is a derivation product of AltTranslate for Safari. See also https://github.com/Tanusai/AltTranslate

History

ver 2.0
Changed translation api to Microsoft Translation API.

ver 1.1
Bug fixes.

ver 1.0
Release.